[Subscribers are referred to Lithuania's presentation on ASF during the 6-7 Feb 2014 meeting of EU's Standing Committee on the Food Chain and Animal Health (SCFCAH) in Brussels (see http://ec.europa.eu/food/committees/regulatory/scfcah/animal_health/docs/20140206-07_asf_lithuania_en.pdf; thanks to Sabine Zentis).

A recent preliminary study of wild boar population dynamics in Turkey/Bulgaria, carried out in the framework of FMD-related epidemiological research, includes some data which may be useful also in relation to other diseases, such as ASF; see at
http://www.fao.org/fileadmin/user_upload/eufmd/40thGeneral_session_documents/40General_Session/App8_FMD_and_wildBoadDKhomenko3.pdf. - Mod.AS

