African swine fever, Russia
-----------------------------
Information received on 11 Feb 2014 from Dr Evgeny Nepoklonov, Deputy Head, Federal Service for Veterinary and Phytosanitary Surveillance, Ministry of Agriculture, Moscow, Russia

